Venture Out
At Cudjoe Cay
Venture Out is a gated community with sixty-nine acres of tropical paradise situated on the island of Cudjoe Key, Florida, a short 23.8 miles north from the southernmost point of the U.S. in Key West Florida.  A 659 Unit private residential condominium association consisting of both RV and mobile homes, both available for short term and long-term rentals.  With exceptional access to both the Atlantic Ocean and the Gulf of Mexico, this tropical island environment is perfect for all your ocean needs.
Bluescape Real Estate
Amenities
Where the Atlantic Ocean is
your backyard
With everything you’ve ever dreamt of at your fingertips, you may not want to ever leave.  All residents are provided with access to the following amenities:
Boat Ramp Access
Marina/Community Store with boat ramp access for all guests.
Ocean Front Pool
81,500 Gallon Heated Pool, 3,000 Gallon Kiddie Pool, and 1,755 Gallon Spa/Jacuzzi.
Lighted Courts
Enjoy our Tennis, Bocce, Pickle Ball, and Basketball courts. All are lighted to enjoy in the evening as well.
TGIF
5 Restroom and Shower Facilities and 5 Laundry Facilities.
Lounge
Community Store
Tiki Point / Swim Lagoon
Tiki God
Come stay with us!
Experience the magic of Cudjoe Key. One of the best places to find a quiet spot to enjoy the nature, observe wildlife or settle back and enjoy a tropical sunset or dip in the ocean. Connect with Bluescape Real Estate, The Official On Site Realtor for All Sales & Rentals, to book.
